  "tasks": [
    {
      "task_name": "Build Tic-Tac-Toe Game",
      "description": "Create a complete tic-tac-toe game application using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Include a 3x3 game board with clickable cells, alternating turns between X and O players, win detection for rows/columns/diagonals, tie game detection, display of current player turn, and a reset/new game button. The game should be fully playable in a web browser.",
